{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-22T04:26:18.768Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the official Claude Cookbook documentation and Anthropic's \"Building Effective Agents\" research, "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"Evaluator-Optimizer\""},{"type":"text","text":" is an "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"orchestration pattern that pairs a generator agent with an evaluator agent in a feedback loop"},{"type":"text","text":", where the generator produces output, the evaluator scores it against defined criteria, and the generator revises based on feedback until quality threshold is met."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What It Is"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The evaluator-optimizer pattern implements a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"quality loop"},{"type":"text","text":": an evaluator critiques outputs and an optimizer (generator) improves them iteratively in a loop until the output meets a quality threshold or max iterations is reached."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Basic Flow"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"text"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"┌──────────────┐\n│   GENERATE   │ ← requirements + (previous critique if iteration > 1)\n└──────┬───────┘\n       │ artifact\n       ▼\n┌──────────────┐\n│   EVALUATE   │ ← rubric + artifact\n└──────┬───────┘\n       │ { score, pass, critique[], suggestions[] }\n       ▼\nscore >= threshold?\n├── YES → ACCEPT artifact\n└── NO → iteration < max?\n     ├── YES → REFINE (feed critique back to generator) → loop\n     └── NO → PRESENT best attempt with warnings"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Components"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Component"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Role"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Characteristics"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generator (Optimizer)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Produces output/draft"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates initial output, revises based on evaluator feedback"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evaluator"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Critiques and scores"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Scores against criteria, provides specific actionable feedback"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Rubric"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluation criteria"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Defines quality dimensions, scoring weights, pass/fail thresholds"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Loop"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Feedback mechanism"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Repeats until threshold met or max iterations reached"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The pattern follows a clear iterative sequence:"}]},{"type":"orderedList","attrs":{"start":1,"type":null},"content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Generate"},{"type":"text","text":" — Generator produces initial output based on task input"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evaluate"},{"type":"text","text":" — Evaluator scores output against defined criteria, provides specific feedback"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Check"},{"type":"text","text":" — If score meets threshold (or max iterations reached), output final version"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Revise"},{"type":"text","text":" — Generator receives evaluator's feedback and produces improved version"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Repeat"},{"type":"text","text":" — Steps 2-4 loop until quality bar is met"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Example: Code Generation"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Generator: \"Write Python function to sort array\"\n- Evaluator: Scores against correctness (35%), completeness (25%), style (20%), safety (20%)\n- Score: 72/100 (below threshold of 80)\n- Feedback: \"Function doesn't handle empty arrays; missing type hints; uses inefficient algorithm\"\n- Generator revises based on feedback\n- Re-evaluate: Score 88/100 (above threshold) → ACCEPT"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"When to Use This Workflow"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluator-optimizer is effective when you have:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Condition"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why It Helps"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Clear evaluation criteria"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluator can objectively score against defined rubric"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Value from iterative refinement"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Quality demonstrably improves with feedback"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"First-draft quality not sufficient"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Single-pass generation doesn't meet quality bar"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Evaluator can check things generator can't"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Run tests, validate against schema, compare to reference"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Cost of iteration < cost of wrong answer"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Better quality justifies more tokens/time"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Good fit examples"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Code generation with strict standards\n- High-stakes docs/comms where tone/precision matter\n- SQL/query generation with security/perf checks"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Bad fit examples"},{"type":"text","text":":\n- Real-time interactions needing immediate responses\n- Tasks with subjective criteria evaluators can't apply consistently\n- Cases where deterministic tools already solve validation (linters, validators)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What to Focus On"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"When implementing evaluator-optimizer, focus on these critical aspects:"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Aspect"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Why It's Important"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Separating \"generate\" from \"judge\""}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Avoids confirmation bias; separate evaluator provides more rigorous feedback"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Stopping criteria"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Prevent infinite loops — use threshold or max iterations"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Turn evaluation into regression tests"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Convert successful evaluations into evals for future validation"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluator-Optimizer vs. Simple Reflection"}]},{"type":"table","content":[{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Aspect"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluator-Optimizer"}]}]},{"type":"tableHeader","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Simple Reflection"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agents"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Two separate agents (generator + evaluator)"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"One agent self-critiques"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Bias"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Avoids confirmation bias"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Risk of self-confirmation bias"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Feedback quality"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"More rigorous, external perspective"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Less objective self-assessment"}]}]}]},{"type":"tableRow","content":[{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Feedback specificity"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Specific, actionable (\"paragraph 3 contradicts data\")"}]}]},{"type":"tableCell","attrs":{"colspan":1,"rowspan":1,"colwidth":null,"align":null},"content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Often vague (\"this needs improvement\")"}]}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key advantage"},{"type":"text","text":": Using a separate evaluator agent avoids confirmation bias and produces more rigorous feedback than simple reflection."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluation Rubric Design"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The rubric should define quality dimensions with weights and scoring criteria:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"markdown"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Score each dimension 0-100, then compute weighted average:\n\n| Dimension  | Weight | What to Check                                      |\n|------------|--------|----------------------------------------------------|\n| Correctness| 35%    | Meets all requirements? Compiles/parses?           |\n| Completeness| 25%   | Edge cases handled? All requirements addressed?    |\n| Style      | 20%    | Follows project conventions? Naming/structure?     |\n| Safety     | 20%    | Security issues? Secrets exposure? Destructive ops?|"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"After each evaluation pass"},{"type":"text","text":", produce structured output:"}]},{"type":"codeBlock","attrs":{"language":"json"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"iteration\": 1,\n  \"score\": 72,\n  \"pass\": false,\n  \"critique\": [\"doesn't handle empty arrays\", \"missing type hints\"],\n  \"suggestions\": [\"add array length check\", \"add @type annotations\"]\n}"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Implementation Best Practices"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. Use Specific, Actionable Feedback"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluator feedback should be specific — not \"this needs improvement\" but \"paragraph 3 contradicts the data in paragraph 1\"."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. Define Clear Stopping Criteria"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Use either:\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Quality threshold"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., score ≥ 80)\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Max iterations"},{"type":"text","text":" (e.g., cap at 3)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. Turn Evaluation into Regression Tests"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Convert successful evaluations into evals for automated future validation."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. Cap Iterations to Avoid Micro-Iterations"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"If iteration 3+ gives tiny improvements, cap iterations lower and move on."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. Use Inline Skills in Claude Code"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluator-optimizer is mapped to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"inline skill ("},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"},{"type":"code"}],"text":"/evaluate"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" in Claude Code — an inline skill that acts as an evidence-based auditor."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Mental Model"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of evaluator-optimizer like a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"writer and editor working together"},{"type":"text","text":": the writer produces a draft, the editor marks it up with specific feedback (\"this paragraph is unclear,\" \"this claim needs a citation\"), and the writer revises. They go back and forth until the piece is publication-ready."}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Key Takeaways"}]},{"type":"bulletList","content":[{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Evaluator-optimizer pairs generator with evaluator in feedback loop for iterative refinement"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Generator produces draft, evaluator scores against criteria, generator revises"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Loop continues until quality threshold met or max iterations exhausted"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Best for: code with strict standards, high-stakes docs, SQL with security checks"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Separate evaluator avoids confirmation bias compared to simple reflection"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Focus on: separating generate/judge, stopping criteria, turning eval into regression tests"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Feedback must be specific and actionable — not vague criticism"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Trade-off: potentially much better quality vs. more tokens, latency, risk of endless micro-iterations"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Quick test: If iteration 3+ gives tiny improvements, cap iterations lower"}]}]},{"type":"listItem","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"In Claude Code: mapped to inline skill ("},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/evaluate"},{"type":"text","text":") for evidence-based auditing"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The pattern provides measurable quality improvement — each iteration either raises the score or the loop terminates."}]}]}}
